                            <h3>What is shopurneeds, 7 days Return & Exchange Policy?</h3>
                            <p>shopurneeds 15 days, returns and exchange policy gives you an option to return or exchange items purchased on https://localhost/project/shopurneeds for any reason within 7 days of receipt of the item. We only ask that you don't use the product and preserve its original condition, tags, and packaging. You are welcome to try on a product but please take adequate measure to preserve its condition.  You need to follow the following conditions:</p>
                            <ul class="alpha">
                                <li>You must be located in INDIA as this facility is not available to patrons located outside INDIA.</li>
                                <li>The products must be returned to shopurneeds within 7 (seven) days from date it is delivered to you.</li>
                                <li>Please check the list of non-returnable or non-exchangeable products at the end of the policy. shopurneeds may update this list from time to time and without any prior intimation to you.</li>
                                <li>The product must be returned in its original condition along with the invoice, all labels, tags, authenticity cards, dust bags, designer boxes, hangers, freebies, if any and other packaging intact sold as a part of the product.</li>
                                <li>Any garment sought to be returned or exchanged, should be unworn or unwashed. Garments that are found to be worn or damaged or soiled will not be accepted for return or exchange.</li>
                                <li>Any footwear sought to be returned or exchanged, should be unused. Thus footwear worn for trial purposes must be done on a carpeted surface. Footwear with worn soles will not be accepted for return or exchange.</li>
                                <li>Products returned under this policy will be subject to quality testing/inspection.</li>
                                <li>If shopurneeds accepts the product returned, you will be entitled to receive refunds in the form of store credit ("shopurneeds Wallet") only.</li>
                                <li>If shopurneeds agrees to exchange the product returned, you will receive shopurneeds Wallet only, which can then be used for purchasing any other merchandise.</li>
                                <li>Notwithstanding anything contained in this policy, shopurneeds reserves a right to reject any request for return and/or exchange of any products without giving any reasons for the same. In such cases, products will be sent back to the customer at the original shipping address.</li>
                                <li>shopurneeds Wallet shall not exceed the value of the product returned and/or exchanged but may be subject to deductions of any benefits for example any discounts availed, shipping or delivery charges waiver, etc., if any. </li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                        <li class="conditions">
                            <h3>What is shopurneeds Returns and Exchange Procedure?</h3>
                            <ul class="alpha">
                                <li>
                                    The returns procedure can also be initiated through https://localhost/project/shopurneeds by following the below mentioned steps:

                                    <ul>
                                        <li>If you made the purchase as a registered user, log in to your account to initiate the process.</li>
                                        <li>If you made the purchase from the Website as a guest, please register on the Website using the same email address provided while purchasing the product so that your products appear in your order history. You can initiate the process of return only if the said product appears in your order history.</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </li>
                                <li>Alternatively, you can initiate the returns/exchange procedure by writing e-mail to <a href="mailto:care@https://localhost/project/shopurneeds">care@https://localhost/project/shopurneeds</a>. shopurneeds will email a ‘Returns/Exchange Request Form’ for you to fill up and email back to shopurneeds.</li>
                                <li>If you are not the actual purchaser but received the product from some shopurneeds customer, (for example as gift), you will have to request the concerned shopurneeds customer to initiate the return process.</li>
                                <li>Upon receiving a ‘Returns/Exchange Request Form’, shopurneeds will generate a ticket number, which will be shared with you. This ticket number must be used in all communication(s) with shopurneeds.  </li>
                                <li>You can return the product by selecting any one of the below options in the ‘Returns/Exchange Request Form’</li>
                                <li>Ship it back to shopurneeds by sending it to the address provided by us. You will be credited worth INR 500 (Rupees one hundred only) in your shopurneeds Wallet towards shipping costs. You will be solely responsible to ensure that the product is delivered to shopurneeds in good condition and shopurneeds will not be held liable for any damage caused to the product during transit.</li>
                                <li>For select pin codes within INDIA, our delivery service can pick-up the product from you. This pick-up service is complimentary and shopurneeds shall not be held liable for any damage caused to the product during transit.</li>
                                <li>shopurneeds will send you a confirmatory e-mail upon receiving the products. Upon undertaking quality test and inspecting the product, shopurneeds will inform you about its decision with respect to acceptance or rejection of the products within 2 (two) working days of receiving the product.</li>
                                <li>If shopurneeds accepts the return/exchange request, value of the product returned/exchanged will be will be credited into shopurneeds Wallet in 3 (three) working days of receiving the product. However, if shopurneeds rejects the return/exchange we will ship the product back to you.</li>
                                <li>If you have any questions, issues, or concerns about your return, or are having trouble with the online returns process, you can email us at <a href="mailto:care@https://localhost/project/shopurneeds">care@https://localhost/project/shopurneeds</a>. </li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                        <li class="conditions">
                            <h3>What is shopurneeds Wallet?</h3>
                            <p>shopurneeds Wallet is valid for a period of 6 (six) months from date of its issue.</p>
                            <p>shopurneeds Wallet can be used to purchase gift cards <b>("shopurneeds Gift Cards")</b> for a value in excess of INR 10,000 (INDIAn Rupees ten thousand only). shopurneeds Gift Cards will also have a validity period of 6 months from date of issue of shopurneeds Gift Cards.</p>
                            <p>Even where the product is purchased by redeeming shopurneeds Gift Cards and such product is returned and/or exchanged, you will be issued shopurneeds Wallet and no reimbursement shall be made into your shopurneeds Gift Card.</p>
                            <p>If the value of products purchased using shopurneeds Wallet:</p>
